findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The functions withdrawDivs(), calcdiv() and compound() uses a loop to iterate through users' deposit list which could be aborted with OUT_OF_GAS exception if there will be a long list.

findings.title: Uninitialized variable used
findings.description: The function withdrawDivs() uses the uninitialized array index FeesKey[50].

findings.title: Potential unauthorized referral restriction
findings.description: stakeStablecoins() function checks only dead address on referral restriction, it also could be zero address.

findings.title: Potential wrong comments in withdrawInitial() function
findings.description: The withdrawInitial() function has wrong comments according to time checking – “_// BETWEEN 30 and 40 DAYS”._

findings.title: Unused DeposMap variable
findings.description: The DeposMap variable is declared but not used.
